{"id": 1334, "genre": 1001, "title": "你觉得哪种表达爱意的方式超可怕？", "description": "你这样不是爱，是精神伤害。（题图来自：Inma Lorente）", "record_count": 7515, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20161116183731qTGesZxuJQX72RSc.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-11-19T17:00:51Z", "options": [{"id": 135424, "content": "电话☎️轰炸", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 839753}, {"id": 172544, "content": "像FBI一样调查你", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 952562}, {"id": 135425, "content": "买卖不成，仁义尽失。", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 729051}, {"id": 136449, "content": "越爱抱的越紧的疼爱方式很可怕", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 844554}, {"id": 135426, "content": "在宿舍楼下摆爱心，", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 769326}, {"id": 135427, "content": "打着爱的名义伤害", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 777542}, {"id": 135428, "content": "看我有多爱你 我把心都掏出来给你看 \n哦 真恶心", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 533504}, {"id": 135429, "content": "十分爱", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 840084}, {"id": 135430, "content": "把自己的观念强加到别人头上的最可怕", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 690354}, {"id": 135431, "content": "瞬间默认自己为对方另一半，并以此要求对方", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 422023}, {"id": 135432, "content": "读作“爱”，写着是完全沾不上边的事物", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1192542}, {"id": 135433, "content": "很久不表达，一旦表达就很极端，如果拒绝就更极端", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 826621}, {"id": 138249, "content": "因为太爱  活生生把自己和对方逼成忧郁症", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 776389}, {"id": 135434, "content": "不得到就要毁灭", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 184580}, {"id": 135435, "content": "木有爱过如何表达", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 811037}, {"id": 135947, "content": "百分百占有，没有给对方一点私人空间的爱最可怕", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 842165}, {"id": 135437, "content": "每天道早安午安晚安 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 840116}, {"id": 135438, "content": "绑架自由", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 821542}, {"id": 135439, "content": "我都是为了你好?", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 360430}, {"id": 135440, "content": "你永远不知道我有多爱你！\n感受不到，你要我怎么知道?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 360430}, {"id": 135441, "content": "秀恩爱。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 835272}, {"id": 135442, "content": "都没说过话，第一句是我爱你…", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 682667}, {"id": 143890, "content": "“我只想要一个苹果而你问都不问我却花了好多好大的心思去搬了一箱梨子给我我不要然后你说我无情冷酷然后哭了把自己感动的稀里哗啦”", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 867018}, {"id": 135443, "content": "明明不爱，还不让你离开", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 733586}, {"id": 135444, "content": "步步紧逼 你退一步 他进两步", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 835251}, {"id": 135445, "content": "single dog don't have anything to say", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 795033}, {"id": 135446, "content": "毫无意义的纠缠", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 734793}, {"id": 135447, "content": "死缠烂打，下跪不起", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 840155}, {"id": 135448, "content": "多喝白开水", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 485775}, {"id": 135193, "content": "为了你的 身心健康 把送你到杨永信手中", "image": null, "praise_count": 260, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 162821}, {"id": 135449, "content": "先让你失望 才给你惊喜 ?", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 277453}, {"id": 136730, "content": "只要不是自己喜欢的人表白，都可怕。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 788952}, {"id": 135195, "content": "为什么大家都说的是被表白的，都是人赢啊。单身狗表示，看别人怎么表达爱意都很可怕", "image": null, "praise_count": 104, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 796687}, {"id": 135451, "content": "为了不让你离开 制造各种谎言", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 840157}, {"id": 157979, "content": "我不能和你乘一趟电梯，我女朋友会吃醋。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 914765}, {"id": 135196, "content": "死也不说", "image": "img/option/option/20161120011220xgzOdB58KQMTasyF.jpg", "praise_count": 361, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 372889}, {"id": 135708, "content": "威胁你", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 841123}, {"id": 135197, "content": "我是为你好", "image": null, "praise_count": 235, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 686426}, {"id": 135198, "content": "以为我也喜欢你", "image": null, "praise_count": 122, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 839411}, {"id": 135454, "content": "自以为对方喜欢你而强势表白给对方下不来台", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 838818}, {"id": 135455, "content": "各种用力过猛的表达，还都不在对方的点上", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 713409}, {"id": 135200, "content": "超大型那种告白我都觉得超级尴尬一点都不浪漫", "image": null, "praise_count": 834, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 835329}, {"id": 135456, "content": "任何公开场合高调示爱不顾及当事人感受的", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 610646}, {"id": 136480, "content": "随便确定关系，这么容易就确定关系，就不会2个月就分手了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 311434}, {"id": 140576, "content": "别人了不喜欢他，他却死缠烂打", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 806696}, {"id": 135201, "content": "喊楼", "image": null, "praise_count": 110, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 680486}, {"id": 135457, "content": "其实并不喜欢他，他却一直贴身跟踪我的一举一动，各种自以为是的评价", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 824926}, {"id": 135203, "content": "坚持叫人起床", "image": null, "praise_count": 57, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 127109}, {"id": 135459, "content": "强行使用自认为高级而真诚的套路", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 833456}, {"id": 136995, "content": "喜欢你，是你的荣幸", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 796836}]}